---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Peter Burgin | Head of Performance & Chief Auctioneer | Ray White Collective"
  description="Peter Burgin, Head of Performance & Chief Auctioneer at Ray White and REIQ Auctioneer of the Year 2010. 20+ years experience, 7,000+ property auctions called including a $10.2m sale at $3.65m above reserve."
>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">
  <div style="position:relative;background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;overflow:hidden;">
    <img
      src="/_vercel/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn6.ep.dynamics.net%2Fs3%2Frw-propertyimages%2Fa665-H3373155-164932053__1758673927-230712-AMY19482.jpg&w=1600&q=70"
      srcset="/_vercel/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn6.ep.dynamics.net%2Fs3%2Frw-propertyimages%2Fa665-H3373155-164932053__1758673927-230712-AMY19482.jpg&w=800&q=70 800w, /_vercel/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn6.ep.dynamics.net%2Fs3%2Frw-propertyimages%2Fa665-H3373155-164932053__1758673927-230712-AMY19482.jpg&w=1600&q=70 1600w"
      sizes="100vw" alt="" decoding="async"
      style="position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:0.32;z-index:0;" />
    <div aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(10,8,6,0.5) 0%,rgba(10,8,6,0.72) 55%,rgba(10,8,6,0.92) 100%);z-index:0;"></div>
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col items-center text-center" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
      <img src="/img/peter-burgin-headshot.jpg" alt="Peter Burgin"
        style="width:160px;height:160px;border-radius:18px;object-fit:cover;border:1.5px solid rgba(197,160,60,0.5);box-shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);margin-bottom:1.5rem;" />
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3rem);font-weight:400;color:#f0ece4;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.01em;margin-bottom:0.55rem;">
        Peter Burgin
      </h1>
      <span style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.6rem;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#f5d07a;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Head of Performance &amp; Chief Auctioneer</span>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1.25rem 2rem;justify-content:center;font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.78rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.82);">
        <a href="tel:+61419782985" data-cta="team_peter_phone" style="color:#f5d07a;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          0419 782 985
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:peter.burgin@raywhite.com" data-cta="team_peter_email" style="color:#f5d07a;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.4rem;">
          <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
          peter.burgin@raywhite.com
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="padding:3rem 0 6rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8" style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--color-text-secondary);line-height:1.9;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">

      <p>With over 20 years experience, Peter has become one of the most respected names in the Real Estate industry.</p>

      <p>Peter has called in excess of 7000 property auctions with the highest sale price of $10.2 million, achieving a result of $3,650,000 above reserve price.</p>

      <p>Peter has built himself a reputation as one of Queensland's best and most highly skilled auctioneers, with expertise in every sector of the property market. Along with this, Peter Burgin has also achieved the coveted, REIQ Auctioneer of the Year Award in 2010.</p>

      <div style="margin-top:2rem;padding-top:2rem;border-top:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.1);">
        <a href="/meet-the-team" style="font-family:var(--font-sans);font-size:0.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-gold);text-decoration:none;">&larr; Back to the team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

</Layout>
